Create a program that initialises an array with the integer values 1 to 10: [Arrays][Slices][For Loops]

1.  Display the array content in ascending sequential order 1 to 10.
2.  Display the array content in descending sequential order 10 to 1.
3.  Count even numbers and odd numbers in increasing and decreasing sequential order.
4.  Display the even and odd count sequences to screen.